00:22:55.896 --> 00:23:00.636 A:middle
And a jungle gym
highlights exploration.

00:23:01.256 --> 00:23:04.736 A:middle
There are multiple ways to get
to the top, there isn't a right

00:23:04.736 --> 00:23:07.396 A:middle
or wrong way to climb,
there isn't a right

00:23:07.396 --> 00:23:10.576 A:middle
or wrong path to take.

