And when I climb, I reach out,
explore, until I find the ropes,

00:23:29.936 --> 00:23:32.046 A:middle
until I find the solution.

00:23:32.146 --> 00:23:37.796 A:middle
There are many, many, many
different ways to climb,

00:23:37.796 --> 00:23:41.966 A:middle
by touch, by sight, by sound.

