If you have a mobility
disability,

00:23:49.026 --> 00:23:53.136 A:middle
you can design an
assistive climbing device.

00:23:53.266 --> 00:23:56.816 A:middle
Exploration values
alternative techniques

00:23:57.386 --> 00:23:59.916 A:middle
and the more open you
are to seeing the world


WEBVTT
