00:24:00.236 --> 00:24:04.886 A:middle
in multiple perspectives,
the more likely you are going

00:24:05.046 --> 00:24:08.686 A:middle
to design, develop
the next big thing.

00:24:09.126 --> 00:24:13.046 A:middle
One area where we rarely
seek innovation is haptics.

00:24:13.246 --> 00:24:16.386 A:middle
And haptics is the concept

00:24:16.496 --> 00:24:19.976 A:middle
of communication
information through touch.

00:24:19.976 --> 00:24:22.686 A:middle
I have an Apple Watch,

00:24:23.356 --> 00:24:26.166 A:middle
and it taps my wrist twice
when I get a message.

00:24:26.296 --> 00:24:28.596 A:middle
And that's a form

00:24:28.596 --> 00:24:32.886 A:middle
of communication based
on haptics, touch.

