I recently went surfing,

00:24:35.846 --> 00:24:41.226 A:middle
and that whole experience
was about haptics.

00:24:41.426 --> 00:24:47.336 A:middle
Here's a photo of
me on a tandem board

00:24:47.336 --> 00:24:49.556 A:middle
and a tandem board
