00:24:49.556 --> 00:24:52.206 A:middle
I'm standing near the front

00:24:53.326 --> 00:24:55.966 A:middle
and in the back is
the surf instructor,

00:24:55.966 --> 00:24:58.266 A:middle
Matt Allen from Maui
Surf Academy.

