00:25:27.216 --> 00:25:29.646 A:middle
of haptics and technology.

00:25:30.916 --> 00:25:36.076 A:middle
Keep exploring, keep
innovating, keep designing apps

00:25:36.596 --> 00:25:39.246 A:middle
that are going to increase
access for everyone.

00:25:39.246 --> 00:25:41.386 A:middle
And as you go through this,

00:25:41.386 --> 00:25:44.266 A:middle
engage with the disability
community,

00:25:44.266 --> 00:25:49.656 A:middle
plan for accessibility from
the start and design knowing

00:25:49.656 --> 00:25:50.716 A:middle
that it's going to benefit you.

00:25:50.716 --> 00:25:54.016 A:middle
Thanks for listening everyone.

